Package: logr
Title: Creates Log Files
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Bosak",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dbosak01@gmail.com")
Description: This package contains functions to help create log files.  The 
    package aims to overcome the difficutly of the base R sink command.  The
    log_print function will print to both the console and the file log, without 
    interfering in other write operations.
